Content:
``> polars convert-time-zone {flags} (time_zone)``
’Щ@db8f9c78d9bf09cf6329cfc43aad278b56c2b0657e00f7ea9a3e6562f409a1b6Щ—Title: title: polars convert-time-zone
Path: Parameters
Content:
``time_zone``
: Timezone for the Datetime Series. Pass 
``null``
 to unset time zone.
